ations of this story can be enriched by a sensitivity to factors such as chronological displacements and variations of focalization.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 01. Dez 2022) 4aErzählung. 4aPolybius. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / Ancient & Classical.2bisacsh  aNarrative.  aPolybius.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Backlist Classics and Near East Studies 2000-2014 (EN)z978311062109908iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Backlist Complete English Language 2000-2014 PART1z978311023857008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Classics and Near East Studies 2000 - 2014z9783110636178oZDB-23-GCN08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK GESAMTPAKET / COMPLETE PACKAGE 2013z9783110317350oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK PACKAGE CLASSICAL STUDIES 2013z9783110317107oZDB-23-DGD08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK PAKET ALTERTUMSWISS. 2013z9783110317091oZDB-23-DGD0 cprintz978311033001440uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311033029840uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110330298423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110330298/original  a978-3-11-023857-0  DGBA Backlist Complete English Language 2000-2014 PART1c2000d2014  a978-3-11-062109-9  DGBA Backlist Classics and Near East Studies 2000-2014 (EN)c2000d2014  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_CL  aEBA_CL_HICS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_CL  aEBA_ECL_HICS  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGDb2013  aZDB-23-DGGb2013  aZDB-23-GCNc2000d2014